The librarian has two desks.

Desk 1 — Working desk (RAM)
self.tasks

This is where all work happens.

Adding.

Deleting.

Searching.

Filtering.

Everything is fast because it's in memory.

Desk 2 — Archive room (disk)
tasks.json

